snippet.description:

snippet.title: DubVision - Backlash (Martin Garrix Edit) [Official Music Video]
snippet.description:
Spinnin' Records proudly presents DubVision - Backlash in the Martin Garrix Edit. Download your copy on Beatport NOW : http://btprt.dj/TY8IzW

Subscribe to Spinnin' TV HERE : http://bit.ly/SPINNINTV

Martin Garrix drops his take on DubVision's Backlash right here on Spinnin'. Those famously huge DubVision chord progressions are mixed seamlessly with Garrix's powerhouse production qualities. Resulting in a larger than life, progressive title of incredible magnitude!

snippet.title: Ummet Ozcan - SMASH! (Official Music Video)
snippet.description:
Ummet Ozcan proudly presents the official video for his new hit SMASH! Download your copy here : http://btprt.dj/1sQMDTM

Subscribe to Spinnin' TV HERE : http://bit.ly/SPINNINTV

Dropped as an ID teaser on YouTube, it was clear this is a hit bound to happen! DJ's loved it straight away and as soon it was clear this was the brand new Ummet Ozcan, fan support exploded as well. So what's SMASH! all about? As you've come to expect from Mr. Ozcan production is unparallelled, melodies are ultra sticky and the drop is HUGE! Amazing work!!!
